These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, woodworking
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, nurse
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, british
2 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, trike
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
2. the nurse is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the owner of the cat is the british##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice     | almond-milk       |
| Hobby         | camping   | woodworking     |
| Job           | analyst | nurse   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | epic  |
| Nationality   | british | indian |
| Pet           | cat      | rabbit     |
| Transport     | trike    | train   |

