.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, cooking
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, journalist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, ambient
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, brazilian
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike
1. the journalist is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the brazilian is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking cola is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | cola    | sprite |
| Hobby         | cooking        | hiking  |
| Job           | designer | journalist  |
| Music-Genre   | ambient            | house    |
| Nationality   | turkish     | brazilian   |
| Pet           | hedgehog         | guinea-pig    |
| Transport     | snowmobile           | trike      |

