.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite
There 2 different types of food: carrot, grapes
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, librarian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, thriller
2 different pets are kept: lizard, horse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, baseball
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
4. the software-developer is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | coffee          | sprite       |
| Food          | grapes   | carrot   |
| Job           | librarian   | software-developer     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | thriller        |
| Pet           | lizard      | horse       |
| Sport         | surfing       | baseball |
| Transport     | bike          | snowmobile |

